1. When your direct report is also a manager, which of the following questions would you ask during your 1:1?
Solution : D. Who's going above and beyond expectations this week?

2. When you're discussing feedback with your direct reports, which of the following would you recommend?
Solution : B. Asking for feedback on your performance

3. Providing support for your direct reports following your 1:1 means:
Solution : C. Taking notes and following up on deliverables between meetings
